Template: config-apt-update/email/configure
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Configure Mail Notification
 If config-apt-update should attempt to configure addresses for notification
 automatically, say Yes.  If not, see /etc/default/config-apt-update for storing
 the mail addresses.

Template: config-apt-update/email/addresses
Type: string
Description: Mailaddresses for notification
 Mailaddresses for update notification separated with whitespaces.
